{"tid":2224161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喂，呢張相足夠揚威海外啦～","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:28:03.000Z","uid":192358,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"000da965c2e25bafd41bf6b5dcca442eeb51961c","tid":2224161,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9zJDAG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9zJDAG.jpg&h=eb53bccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推上國際啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【1445 太子站】「Lunch哥」中學生David今日發起「太子站和你睇蘋果」活動，現場僅得David一人坐在椅子閱報。逾10名警員在場戒備，同時有多名港鐵職員在場，並向David指其活動可能影響其他乘客，警員隨後一度拉橙帶設封鎖線。<br />\n<br />\n及後藍絲KOL石房有踩場，雙方稍有口角，最終港鐵職員警告David若不離開將會發出告票，David惟有被迫離開。"},{"pid":"09eb06dac4e458b804abebf67b9867ca25c1ceba","tid":2224161,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3332e8933fa3bb0af8e5e9fbfba8ba0910e7af8f","tid":2224161,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"b4df99beef73d64c4a51601824b6148081bec0e2","tid":2224161,"uid":57671,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7db9c4be3d615182417c708d043cbcc4c199577b","tid":2224161,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"熱狗/某d黃絲channel:  lunch 哥收錢做野, 唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53fe0c87a640038c48042d0715dee32d3c050be","tid":2224161,"uid":192358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7db9c4be3d615182417c708d043cbcc4c199577b","tid":2224161,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:22:31.0